"Cannot reach autonomous inference: even if all %(unclassified)d "
"unclassified faces are target matches, you would have "
"%(potential)d/%(min)d confirmed — below the threshold."
msgstr ""
"No se puede alcanzar la inferencia autónoma: incluso si todos los "
"%(unclassified)d rostros sin clasificar coinciden, tendría "
"%(potential)d/%(min)d confirmados — por debajo del umbral."

